markdownRemark.html:
An interactive geo quiz game app to guess town/city name from given choices and a unmarked map. This is inspired from a geo-quiz by the Telegraph.

The game is available to play at http://jabran.me/guess-where

frontmatter.title: Guess where – an interactive geo quiz
